Class XmlSeries

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mindfusion.charting.XmlSeries
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Series

    public class XmlSeries
extends java.lang.Object
implements Series
    Represents a series whose data items are retrieved from an XML document.
